descriptionHTML:
Pimp your watch with Jamaica Flag Watch Face. Clean and fast digital interface for everyday use.

INSTRUCTION:

1. Install Watch Face
2. Go to Android Wear Application
3. Choose Jamaica Watch Face
4. Enjoy!

The Jamaica watchface has been tested on Moto 360, LG G Watch R, ASUS ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch and other.
